I could probably easily fix this, but unless there are serious complaints this probably won't be fixed.\
\
- 
\f2\i\b It doesn't work with 3rd-party controllers
\f0\i0\b0 , (and probably wheels, remote control, headset, etc). These 
\f2\i\b can
\f0\i0\b0  be supported, since (I believe) they all use the same hardware spec. \
\
